{"body": "This section applies for the purposes of this Chapter.\n\u201cAdjusted net income\u201d of a person for a tax year means the person's adjusted net income for that tax year as determined under section 58 of ITA 2007.\n\u201cWeek\u201d means a period of 7 days beginning with a Monday; and a week is in a tax year if (and only if) the Monday with which it begins is in the tax year.", "citation_label": "2003 c. 1 s. 681H", "citation_path": "uk/statute/ukpga/2003/1/681H", "document_class": "statute", "expression_date": "2026-04-06", "heading": "Section 681H", "id": "378f888f-f870-5574-a264-0c727a291e7f", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "1", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "681H", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "ukpga", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2003"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "section", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "2003 c. 1 s. 681H", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W", "S", "N.I."], "references_to": ["ukpga/2003/1"], "retrieved_at": null}, "source_as_of": "2026-07-05", "source_document_id": "ukpga/2003/1", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2003/1/section/681H", "source_path": "sources/uk/statute/2026-07-05-uk-hicbc-itepa/ukpga/2003/1/section-681H.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2003/1/section/681H", "version": "2026-07-05-uk-hicbc-itepa"}
